GAP test

HOW TO RUN
1. Missing Letters

$> ruby MissingLetters.rb "A quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog"

$> ruby MissingLetters.rb "A slow yellow fox crawls under the proactive dog"
bjkmqz 
$> ruby MissingLetters.rb "Lions, and tigers, and bears, oh my\!"
cfjklpquvwxz

****
NOTE: Please note that the ! simbol needs to be escaped on the linux console.
****

$> ruby MissingLetters.rb ""
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz

2. Animation

$> ruby Animation.rb 2 "...R...."
...X....
.....X..
.......X
........

$> ruby Animation.rb 3  "RR..LRL"
XX..XXX
.X.XX..
X.....X
.......

ruby Animation.rb 2,  "LRLR.LRLR"
XXXX.XXXX
